  <p>The Experience Flask can store a maximum of 100 experience levels.</p>
  <p>
    To put in the experience, you need an
    <a href="/xp-transfer-table">Experience Transfer Table</a>. When the experience is stored in the
    flask you can access it by drinking from the flask. You do not have to do so however, as it also
    works when it is still sitting on the
    <a href="/xp-transfer-table">Experience Transfer Table</a>.
  </p>
